data.description: Nestled in the heart of Richfield, off Nicollet Ave, this timeless residence exudes classic charm and an enduring connection to the city. This home embodies comfort and practicality with four bedrooms (including the upper half-story), one bath, and ample space for two cars plus tools in the garage. The gleaming hardwood floors throughout the home evoke a sense of warmth and character, while the inviting fireplace serves as the centerpiece of the living area, creating a cozy ambiance perfect for gatherings during those chilly Minnesota evenings. The well-maintained home has a larger and open kitchen area and two bedrooms on the main floor. Situated in a serene neighborhood, this property offers both privacy and connectivity, providing a haven for relaxation while conveniently located near urban amenities, 15 minutes to both downtown Minneapolis and the airport. You'll also be able to come in and bring your own updates and finishing touches!
